    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I am so excited to show you this absolute gem. Honestly, it\u2019s in such incredible shape that it still looks and smells brand new! It\u2019s been pampered and garage-kept since day one, and you won\u2019t find a single scratch or blemish on it. If you\u2019ve been looking for perfection, this is the one. I\u2019d love for it to go to someone who will appreciate it as much as I have\u2014come take a look and see for yourself!",
