    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This E92 M3 is an impeccable example of the legendary S65 platform, featuring a high-revving 4.0L naturally aspirated V8 with individual throttle bodies and an 8,400 RPM redline. Power is routed through a precise 6-speed manual transmission to the rear wheels via the M Variable Differential Lock. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), providing exceptional lateral grip and damping transitions. This specimen has undergone comprehensive preventative maintenance, including rod bearing replacement and throttle actuator service. The factory finish is flawless, and the undercarriage shows zero signs of subframe fatigue or oxidation, representing a true collector-grade mechanical state.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. No scratches or mechanical issues. Complete service history included.",
      "price": 46500.0,
