      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute pride and joy. Honestly, this car is in such incredible shape, it feels like it just rolled off the showroom floor! I\u2019ve babied it since day one\u2014always garaged and kept spotless inside and out. It drives like a dream and looks even better in person. If you\u2019re looking for something that\u2019s basically brand new without the new-car sticker shock, this is definitely the one for you! Come take a look, you won't be disappointed!",
      "price": 44500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
