      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 4
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Offering a collector-grade 2002 BMW M3 (E46) that defines mechanical perfection. This example features the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six, utilizing individual throttle bodies and a dual-VANOS system to deliver a seamless 8,000 RPM powerband. Power is routed through a precise Getrag 6-speed manual transmission to a variable M differential lock, ensuring optimal torque distribution. The chassis is impeccably preserved, with a verified crack-free subframe and a suspension geometry that remains as taut as the day it left Regensburg. Finished in Carbon Black over Nappa leather, the aesthetic condition is flawless, retaining factory paint depth and a cabin devoid of typical bolster wear or trim degradation. A peerless example for the discerning enthusiast who demands uncompromised performance and provenance.",
